{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"12143c4c9a","title":"决战动员令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4c0945cf4d","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":18,"articleId":"12143c4c9a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"27650d6b7c","type":"paragraph","text":"决战动员令","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"12143c4c9a"},{"id":"35e8cad1e8","type":"paragraph","text":"1936年11月18日）一、二、四方面军各兵团军事政治首长钓鉴：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"12143c4c9a"},{"id":"d404f99d2d","type":"paragraph","text":"从明日起粉碎蒋介石进攻的决战，各首长务须以最坚决的决心，最负责的忠实与最吃苦耐心的意志去执行。而且要谅谅告诉下级首长转告于全体战斗员，每人都照着你们的决心，惠忧与意志，服从命令，英勇作战，克服任何的困难，并准备连续的战斗。因为当前的这一个战斗，关系于苏维埃，关系于中国，都是非常之大的，而敌人的弱点我们的优点又都是很多的。我们一定要不怕疲劳，要勇敢冲锋，多提仔房，多缴枪炮，粉碎这一进攻，开展新的局面，以三个方面军会合于西北苏区的胜利作第一个赠献给全苏区的人民的礼物","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"12143c4c9a"},{"id":"6d05b8fc0c","type":"paragraph","text":"红军胜利万岁！苏维埃胜利方岁！抗日民族战争方岁！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"12143c4c9a"},{"id":"b1a2fa87b4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东张国泰彭德怀任强时朱德周恩来贺龙","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"12143c4c9a"}],"page":{"id":"ac6552d176","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"12143c4c9a","start":4,"end":4}}}},"__N_SSG":true}